OL,3,COil prices rise after US strikes on
OL,4,CIran nuclear sites
OL,6,FOil prices have risen following the
OL,7,FUS's strikes on three Iranian nuclear
OL,8,Fsites in a major escalation of the
OL,9,FIran-Israel conflict.
OL,11,FThe price of Brent crude oil, the
OL,12,Ftraditional benchmark global oil
OL,13,Fprice, was up 2% at $78.52 a barrel on
OL,14,FMonday. US crude also jumped, gaining
OL,15,F2% to $75.34 a barrel by midday in
OL,16,FAsia.
