OL,6,FThe attacks by the United States on
OL,7,FSaturday, which President Donald Trump
OL,8,Fclaimed caused "monumental damage",
OL,9,Fraised the stakes in the war between
OL,10,FIsrael and Iran.
OL,12,FThe conflict began with an Israeli
OL,13,Fattack against Iran on June 13 that
OL,14,Fsent oil prices yo-yoing and rattled
OL,15,Fother markets.
OL,17,FIran is a major producer of oil and
OL,18,Falso sits on the narrow Strait of
OL,19,FHormuz, through which much of the
OL,20,Fworld's crude passes.
