OL,6,FClosing off the waterway would be
OL,7,Ftechnically difficult to pull off, but
OL,8,Fit could severely disrupt transit
OL,9,Fthrough it, sending insurance rates
OL,10,Fspiking and making shippers nervous to
OL,11,Fmove without US Navy escorts.
OL,13,FForeign Secretary David Lammy said he
OL,14,Fhad told Iran it would be a "mistake"
OL,15,Fto blockade the Strait of Hormuz, as
OL,16,Fhe urged Iran to take the "off-ramp"
OL,17,Fand engage in diplomacy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
