OL,6,FLammy also stated it would be a
OL,7,F"catastrophic mistake" for Tehran to
OL,8,Ffire at US bases in the region in
OL,9,Fresponse to the US attack on Iranian
OL,10,Fnuclear facilities.
OL,12,FThe foreign secretary told BBC
OL,13,FBreakfast: "It would be a catastrophic
OL,14,Fmistake. It would be a mistake to
OL,15,Fblockade the Strait of Hormuz."
OL,17,FHe said he thinks his counterpart
OL,18,F"gets that and understands that".
