OL,6,F"The situation remains highly fluid,
OL,7,Fand much hinges on whether Tehran opts
OL,8,Ffor a restrained reaction or a more
OL,9,Faggressive course of action," Kristian
OL,10,FKerr, head of macro strategy at LPL
OL,11,FFinancial in Charlotte, North
OL,12,FCarolina, said.
OL,14,FIran may be reluctant to close down
OL,15,Fthe waterway because it uses the
OL,16,Fstrait to transport its own crude,
OL,17,Fmostly to China, and oil is a major
OL,18,Frevenue source for the regime.
