OL,6,F"It's a scorched earth possibility, a
OL,7,FSherman-burning-Atlanta move," said
OL,8,FTom Kloza, chief market analyst at
OL,9,FTurner Mason & Co. "It's not probable."
OL,11,FMr Kloza thinks oil futures will ease
OL,12,Fback down after initial fears blow
OL,13,Fover.
OL,15,FEd Yardeni, a long-time analyst,
OL,16,Fagreed, writing in a report that
OL,17,FTehran leaders would likely hold back.
