OL,6,F"They aren't crazy," he wrote in a
OL,7,Fnote to investors Sunday. "The price
OL,8,Fof oil should fall and stock markets
OL,9,Faround the world should climb higher."
OL,11,FEconomists at Panmure Liberum have
OL,12,Fcalculated the global impact if Iran
OL,13,Fwere to close to the strait, finding
OL,14,Fit could disrupt about a fifth of
OL,15,Fglobal oil and a fifth of global gas
OL,16,Fshipments.
